quran[64]{c,v,t}:
  84,1,Pamene thambo lidzang’ambika
  84,2,Ndipo limva ndi kumvera Ambuye wake ndipo ling’ambikadi
  84,3,Pamene nthaka idzatambasulidwa
  84,4,Ndi kutulutsa zonse zimene zinakwiriridwa m’kati mwake ndi kukhala yopanda kanthu
  84,5,Ndipo limva ndi kumvera Ambuye wake ndipo ling’ambikadi
  84,6,oh iwe munthu! Ndithudi iwe uli kubwerera kupita kwa Ambuye wako ndi ntchito zako. Kubwerera kotsimikizidwa. Motero udzakumana nazo
  84,7,Koma Iye amene adzapatsidwa Buku lake m’dzanja lamanja
  84,8,Adzawerengedwa mosavuta
  84,9,Ndipo adzabwerera kwa anthu ake ndi chisangalalo
  84,10,Koma iye amene adzapatsidwa buku lake kumbuyo kwake
  84,11,Iye adzalira
  84,12,Ndipo akalowa ku moto walawi – lawi ku Gahena
  84,13,Ndithudi iye adali wansangala pakati pa anthu ake
  84,14,Ndithudi iye anali kuganiza kuti sadzabwerera kwa Mulungu
  84,15,Inde! Ndithudi Ambuye wake anali kuona zonse zimene iye ankachita
  84,16,Ine ndilumbira pali kufiira kwa kulowa kwa dzuwa
  84,17,Ndi pali usiku ndi zonse zimene umabweretsa mu mdima
  84,18,Ndi pali mwezi pamene ufika pa chimake penipeni
  84,19,"Ndipo inu, ndithudi, mudzayenda kupita kutsogolo, kuchoka apa ndi kufika apo"
  84,20,Kodi ndi chifukwa chiyani choti iwo alibe chikhulupiriro
  84,21,Ndipo pamene Korani ili kuwerengedwa kwa iwo sagwa pansi. Al-Buruj
  84,22,Iyayi! Koma anthu osakhulupirira amalikana
  84,23,Ndipo Mulungu amadziwa zinthu zonse zimene amasonkhanitsa
  84,24,Choncho auze iwo za chilango chowawa
  84,25,"Kupatula okhawo amene akhulupirira ndi kumachita ntchito zabwino, chifukwa iwo ali ndi malipiro opanda malire"
  85,1,Pali kumwamba kumene kuli nyenyezi zikulu zikulu
  85,2,Pali tsiku lolonjezedwa
  85,3,Pali tsiku la umboni ndi tsiku loperekedwa umboni
  85,4,wotembereredwa anali anthu amene anakumba ngalande
  85,5,Imene munali moto woyaka
  85,6,Pamene akhala moizungulira
  85,7,Ndipo iwo adachitira umboni pa zomwe amachitira anthu okhulupirira
  85,8,"Iwo analibe mlandu wina uliwonse ndi anthuwa kupatula kuti anali kukhulupirira mwa Mulungu mmodzi yekha, Mwini mphamvu zonse, Mwini kuyamikidwa"
  85,9,Mwini Ufumu wakumwamba ndi dziko lapansi! Ndipo Mulungu ndi mboni pa chilichonse
  85,10,"Ndithudi onse amene adazunza amuna okhulupirira, ndi akazi okhulupilira ndipo salapa machimo awo, adzalandira chilango chowawa cha moto woyaka wa ku Gahena"
  85,11,Ndithu onse amene akhulupirira ndi kuchita ntchito zabwino adzakhala m’minda imene ili ndi mitsinje ya madzi oyenda. Kumeneko ndiko kupambana kwakukulu
  85,12,Ndithudi chilango cha Ambuye wako ndi chowawa
  85,13,Ndithudi Iye ndiye amene amayambitsa chilengedwe ndipo adzachibwereza patsiku louka kwa akufa
  85,14,Ndipo Iye ndi wokhululuka ndi wachikondi chodzadza
  85,15,"Mwini wake wa Mpando wachifumu, Wolemekezeka"
  85,16,Iye amachita chimene afuna
  85,17,Kodi iwe siudamve za asirikali
  85,18,A Farao ndi a Thamoud
  85,19,Iyayi! Koma anthu osakhulupirira amazikana
  85,20,Ndipo Mulungu amawazungulira onse
  85,21,Iyayi! Ili ndi Buku loyera la Korani
  85,22,Lolembedwa m’Buku lotetezedwa
  86,1,Pali kumwamba ndi pali Nyenyezi yowala
  86,2,Kodi chidzakudziwitsa kuti Nyenyezi yowala ndi chiani
  86,3,Ndi Nyenyezi yowala kothobwetsa maso
  86,4,Ndithudi moyo uliwonse uli ndi mtetezi wake
  86,5,Tamulekani munthu kuti aganize kuti adalengedwa kuchokera ku chiyani
  86,6,Iye adalengedwa kuchokera ku madzi otuluka
  86,7,Amene amatuluka kuchokera pakati pa pfupa la munsana ndi nthiti
  86,8,Ndithudi Iye ali ndi mphamvu zomudzutsa
  86,9,Pa tsiku limene zinthu zobisika zidzayesedwa
  86,10,Ndipo adzakhala wopanda mphamvu kapena womuthandiza
  86,11,Pali mtambo umene umapereka mvula kawiri kawiri
  86,12,Ndi pali dziko lapansi limene limang’ambika
  86,13,Ndithudi! Awa ndi mawu amene amasiyanitsa
  86,14,Si nthabwala ayi
  86,15,"Ndithudi iwo Al-A’la\t649 ali kukonza chiwembu"
  86,16,Ndipo Inenso ndili kukonza chiwembu
  86,17,Motero apatse nthawi anthu osakhulupirira. Ndipo chita nawo mwamtendere pa kanthawi kochepa